Semantic Tags


ğŸ”¹ <header>

Contains intro content + navigation

Helps screen readers understand page structure

ğŸ”¹ <nav>

Used only for navigation links

Improves accessibility & SEO

ğŸ”¹ <main>

Wraps the main content

There should be only one <main> per page

ğŸ”¹ <section>

Groups related content

Used instead of random <div>s

ğŸ”¹ <article>

Used for independent content (education block)

ğŸ”¹ <footer>

Contains contact info, copyright

Clearly separates page ending content

ğŸ‘‰ Why not <div>?
Because <div> has no meaning, semantic tags give context + accessibility.
